      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KANENA PROVLIMA (8) was good when stepping away from the city last time, coming from a similar draw to this for a 4.5m second to Group performer Ripp in the Bathurst Mayors Cup. Strikes at 50 per cent at this shorter distance and with his A-game he has the class to take this out. CYA ART NZ (9) hasn't featured in two runs this campaign but they have been against stronger opposition at Menangle. Won the Group 1 Len Smith Mile last season and also placed in an Inter Dominion final so his best is very good. ROCKTAGONAL (5) has come from wider barriers than this for good performances in his last two outings at Menangle and scored back-to-back Tamworth wins prior. Worth including. The good draw may see improvement from PET KITTY (2).",
